Compute the Hessenberg decomposition of the matrix @var{A}.

The Hessenberg decomposition is
@tex
$$
A = PHP^T
$$
where $P$ is a square unitary matrix ($P^TP = I$), and $H$
is upper Hessenberg ($H_{i,j} = 0, \forall i \ge j+1$).
